25|$|HBO Films {{produced}} a 79-minute documentary titled The Journalist and the Jihadi: The Murder of Daniel Pearl. It premiered on HBO on October 10, 2006. The documentary chronicles Pearl's life and death, and features extensive interviews with his immediate family. It is narrated by <b>Christiane</b> <b>Amanpour,</b> and {{was nominated for}} two Emmy Awards.|$|E
